<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 02:09:01 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>克劳德寓言5和克劳德神话5</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/claude-fable-5-and-claude-mythos-5</link><description>虽然《神话 5》对于受限制的政府和值得信赖的企业合作伙伴在很大程度上仍然不受限制，但《神鬼寓言 5》则被包裹在复杂的安全范围内。如果《神鬼寓言 5》检测到提示转向高风险向量（例如网络战漏洞、高级生物学或化学合成），它不仅仅会给出一般性的“我无法回答这个问题”错误。相反，查询会无缝回退到 Claude Opus 4.8（Anthropic 的第二个最强大的模型）来安全地处理响应。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/claude-fable-5-and-claude-mythos-5.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 02:08:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/claude-fable-5-and-claude-mythos-5</guid></item><item><title>研究人员触发睡眠对清醒大脑部分的恢复作用</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/researchers-trigger-sleeps-restorative-effect-in-parts-of-the-awake-brain</link><description>威斯康星大学麦迪逊分校的科学家通过人工诱导慢波大脑活动，成功地在清醒小鼠身上复制了深度睡眠的一些恢复作用。研究人员利用光遗传学控制特定神经元，触发了模仿 NREM 睡眠阶段的局部皮层活动，该阶段负责突触稳态和神经连接的重组。这种有针对性的刺激显着减少了小鼠长时间清醒后的疲劳迹象，并改善了记忆保留和认知能力。虽然研究人员警告说，这种技术并不能替代自然睡眠，但研究结果表明，局部神经刺激可以在长时间清醒期间有效保护大脑功能。未来的研究旨在探索是否可以通过非侵入性方法（例如经颅电刺激）在人类身上实现类似的认知益处。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/researchers-trigger-sleeps-restorative-effect-in-parts-of-the-awake-brain.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 01:53:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/researchers-trigger-sleeps-restorative-effect-in-parts-of-the-awake-brain</guid></item><item><title>科学家重新连接供体干细胞以智胜侵袭性血癌</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/scientists-rewire-donor-stem-cells-to-outsmart-aggressive-blood-cancers</link><description>研究人员测试了一种基因编辑的干细胞移植，旨在保护健康的造血细胞免受强大的癌症靶向免疫疗法的影响。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-rewire-donor-stem-cells-to-outsmart-aggressive-blood-cancers.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 01:38:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/scientists-rewire-donor-stem-cells-to-outsmart-aggressive-blood-cancers</guid></item><item><title>太空植物可能成为宇航员未来的药房</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/space-plants-could-be-future-pharmacies-for-astronauts</link><description>科学家们成功测试了一种在模拟太空条件下从植物中获取救生药物的非破坏性方法，从而能够为长期任务按需生产药物。 [ &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/space-plants-could-be-future-pharmacies-for-astronauts.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 01:23:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/space-plants-could-be-future-pharmacies-for-astronauts</guid></item><item><title>独家|百事公司在亚利桑那州运营 35 辆无人驾驶卡车，运送多力多滋和菲多利薯条</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/exclusive-pepsico-operating-35-driverless-trucks-in-arizona-delivering-doritos-and-frito-lay-chips</link><description>百事公司在亚利桑那州、德克萨斯州和阿肯色州有 41 辆卡车在路上行驶，使该技术成为主流。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/exclusive-pepsico-operating-35-driverless-trucks-in-arizona-delivering-doritos-and-frito-lay-chips.gif" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 01:08:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/exclusive-pepsico-operating-35-driverless-trucks-in-arizona-delivering-doritos-and-frito-lay-chips</guid></item><item><title>新试点工厂可在 30 分钟内将未分类的塑料废物转化为石油</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/new-pilot-plant-converts-unsorted-plastic-waste-into-oil-in-30-mins</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 00:53:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/new-pilot-plant-converts-unsorted-plastic-waste-into-oil-in-30-mins</guid></item><item><title>巅峰协议：山地长寿静修</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/peak-protocol-mountain-longevity-retreat</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 00:38:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/peak-protocol-mountain-longevity-retreat</guid></item><item><title>量子存储器超越了存储未知量子操作的经典限制</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/quantum-memory-surpasses-classical-limits-for-storing-unknown-quantum-operations</link><description>量子存储器是利用量子力学效应存储和检索信息的系统，在某些现有任务上可以超越经典存储系统。然而，这些有前途的存储器还可以完成对于经典系统来说非常困难或不可能的操作，包括所谓的等距通道的存储和检索。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/quantum-memory-surpasses-classical-limits-for-storing-unknown-quantum-operations.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 00:23:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/quantum-memory-surpasses-classical-limits-for-storing-unknown-quantum-operations</guid></item><item><title>CERN 的凌晨 3 点量子模拟意外揭示了现实的隐藏层</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/cerns-3-am-quantum-simulation-accidentally-revealed-a-hidden-layer-of-reality</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 14:25:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/cerns-3-am-quantum-simulation-accidentally-revealed-a-hidden-layer-of-reality</guid></item><item><title>量子纠缠真的存在吗？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/is-quantum-entanglement-even-real</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 14:10:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/is-quantum-entanglement-even-real</guid></item></channel></rss>